The paper focuses on attention mechanisms in deep learning models for visual reasoning tasks, specifically on abstract cognitive tasks on image data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of attention mechanisms and deep learning models for this task suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
